Body:
Description: IDM Team unable login to StealthAudit using PCDAAIDMR01 due to this ID exist only in Local AD not inside the system. 
Username PCDAAIDMR01 created to reset and maintain user access.

Please advise if need recreate username or we just can reset password to solve the issue. 

Fyi, there are on going activity performed by server team to integrate child AD servers to the new servers. Not really sure if this activity that caused this issue. 
We also do not have visibility on the details activity to share with you. 

FYI, multiple users unable to login the the StealthAudit at this moment and required for password reset if possible.
What We've Learned Updated: The issue is present internally at the customer end and not our application end
Since the issue was resolved by the customer's team internally and the issue doesn't seem to be linked with our product, the Ticket closing format from TextExpander was not followed.
